headline: Chipotle Mexican Grill Stock: Is CMG Underperforming the Consumer Cyclical Sector?
summary: While Chipotle Mexican Grill has underperformed relative to its sector over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook on the stock’s prospects.

headline: Is Chipotle Mexican Grill (CMG) Pricing Look Reasonable After A 27.9% One Year Decline
summary: If you are wondering whether Chipotle Mexican Grill is fairly priced or not, you are in the right place as we are about to unpack what the current share price could mean for long term investors. Chipotle's share price recently closed at US$38.05, with returns of 0.2% over the past week, a 4.0% decline over the last 30 days, 1.5% year to date, and a 27.9% decline over the past year, compared with gains of 27.2% over 3 years and 40.8% over 5 years.
